                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "eab9d3500a3a4feea90da",
                    "stepText": "Now, to determine the heat produced in the extension cord, select the correct formula that relates heat production to the square of the current and the resistance.",
                    "stepText2": "",
